Bahut badiya! âœ… Ab tum Kafka pe JSON object bhejna aur consume karna chahte ho â€” aur sath hi Spring Kafka vs Kafka Client ka difference samajhna chahte ho.

ğŸ§± Part 1: Kafka Me Object (JSON) Bhejna Aur Consume Karna
ğŸ¯ Use Case:
Maan lo tumhare paas LocationDTO naam ka object hai:

public class LocationDTO {
    private String userId;
    private String city;

    // Getters, Setters, Constructors
}
âœ… Step-by-Step: Object as JSON using Spring Kafka
ğŸ“¦ Step 1: Dependency (already honi chahiye)
<dependency>
    <groupId>org.springframework.kafka</groupId>
    <artifactId>spring-kafka</artifactId>
</dependency>
<dependency>
    <groupId>com.fasterxml.jackson.core</groupId>
    <artifactId>jackson-databind</artifactId>
